OL,6,FThe boss of the CBI, one of the UK's
OL,7,Flargest business groups, has been
OL,8,Fsacked after an investigation into
OL,9,Fcomplaints about his conduct at work.
OL,11,FTony Danker, director-general of
OL,12,FConfederation of British Industry,
OL,13,Fhas been dismissed with immediate
OL,14,Feffect and will be replaced by Rain
OL,15,FNewton-Smith.
